name: Stanley Blake Jr.
text: This is a quite gym with a pool, sauna, steam room, and gym floor, which is layed out with both free weights, machines, and treadmills.They also have a massage team that goes under the name Angel's Touch Massage.

name: Gidgett Overton
text: Friendly staff, exercise classes for all ages, racquetball courts/games are fun to watch, and the steam room and sauna are a great place to unwind in after a great workout!

name: Dawn Santiago
text: I love the people!! They are very friendly and polite.

name: Tamara Roden
text: I just went there Sat n I worked out after I worked out I went swimming n got in the hot tub n after that got a shower n after we left I noticed my hair that it turned it green n I called them n said wash it alot of times n it should come out well it didn't so I tried something eles it's starting to bring the green out it's still in thier I'm working on getting it out so if I was u I would be careful with anything to do with there water I will workout thier but I will not be using it trusting anything with thiet water again not even thier showers

name: Todd Shaw
text: Great price, friendly staff, clean facilities, and awesome racquetball courts.

resp.text: Thank you Greg!!  Hope you will return to SportsFit soon!!

name: Roberto Gay
text: They've got everything you want and then some.

name: Jayne Rainey
text: Clean, not pushed to do things
